content: I’m happy for you .  And if i told you that i understood .  I just wish we could’ve met somewhere in the middle .  Discussing a common possibility of the future .  Since we didn’t , I’m stuck with assumptions .  For so many years we kneaded together .  something that was suppose to keep us warm .
